Dr Hunt took over this practice when Dr Faulkenburg retired. He has been here since April 1 and I have yet to see him. I was scheduled to get my blood work and see him. The day of my appt, office called and said he would not be in that afternoon. They rescheduled me a month away. Today was my appt at 1:40pm. I signed in and waited. They called back several patients that were scheduled AFTER me. I went to front desk and when the woman finally put her phone call on hold and came up to window, I explained what the problem was, and she said we go by computer schedule not sign in sheet. You'll be called when it is your turn. With that, she slammed the sliding glass window shut and went back to her phone call. I walked out and will find a doctor that sees his patients within a reasonable time and has staff that cares about patients and is not so rude!
